The '''Baobab School of Speed-Learning''' was a division of the [[Baobab Archives]]. Devoted to the education of beings in short amounts of time, the school specialized in the teaching of languages. This is not surprising, due to the Archives' penchant for [[Wikipedia:philology|philology]], and the [[Huttese/Legends|Huttese]] program at this institution was particularly popular.

